Smart Pointer in Rust Box Box 是最简单的智能指针，它允许你将一个值放在堆上而不是栈上。
fn main() { let f1 = foo { bar: 32 }; let f2 = Box::new(foo { bar: 11 }); println!(&#34;address on stack: {:p}&#34;, &amp;f1); println!(&#34;address on heap: {:p}&#34;, f2); println!(&#34;address of box(on stack): {:p}&#34;, &amp;f2); } struct foo { bar: i32, } // address on stack: 0x7ffd34540f0c // address on heap: 0x57d39e669ba0 // address of box(on stack): 0x7ffd34540f10 Box 只提供了间接存储和堆分配，除此之外没有其他特殊功能。
